Antennae (
Fig. 3A
), short, scape securiform, pedicel short and rounded, flagellomeres I to IV similar, wider than long, flagellomere V strongly transverse, about three times as wide as long, antennal club (flagellomeres VI–VIII) covered with dense short yellow hairs.

